sonarr_episodefile_episodeoverviews: Erulogs and Sirus goes on a killing spree, killing on what it looks like to be hundred of Golden Dragons.  Lina manages to get away to Filia, seeing if she could get the last item.  Filia can't so Lina decides to use the Laguna Blade spell to try and break the barrier.  It works, and Lina takes a hold of the cross bow, she fires a shot, displaying it's power.
